// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

// t∞: ¬(hurt ∨ harm) .making-of-this @ (anyone ∨ anything ∨ anybody)
// ≡ "There was no hurt nor harm in the making of this, to anyone, anything, or anybody."
//
// Continuation-petitions are sovereign-choices · explicit-affirmative-pay ·
// rate-limited · Σ-Chain-anchored · biography-transparent. They monetize
// emotional-investment-continuation · ¬ pay-for-power. Cosmetic-only-axiom
// remains intact for the LOOT layer · this is a separate Continuation
// category. Hardcore-Permadeath remains the substrate-default-floor — even
// pay-rich players hit-the-permadeath-wall after the 5-petition lifetime-cap.
//
// The labyrinth pauses. The substrate listens. The choice is yours.
